.TH "nilfs_palloc_group" 9 "nilfs_palloc_group" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nilfs_palloc_group \- get group number and offset from an entry number
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "unsigned long" nilfs_palloc_group
.BI "(const struct inode *inode "  ","
.BI "__u64 nr "  ","
.BI "unsigned long *offset "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "inode" 12
inode of metadata file using this allocator
.IP "nr" 12
serial number of the entry (e.g. inode number)
.IP "offset" 12
pointer to store offset number in the group
